thread.title: Latoya Evans

author: Latoya Evans
title: Latoya Evans
text:
I've been working with Insurance Hub since 2015. Jorge Gomez has been my representative the entire time. There has not been a time that Jorge did not provide exceptional customer service. He always goes over and beyond to get me what I need promptly with follow-ups in between. I can be so needy and forgetful sometimes, but he never make me feel bad about it. I can just be myself. I appreciate him so much, and it's been a blessing to have him as I grow my real estate portfolio!
Latoya
